-----------------------------
TkCommissioner for CC7 at P5
-----------------------------

This is the updated version of the TkCommissioner tool used for the commissioning of the CMS silicon strip tracker.

###### Installation procedure

Prerequisites --> installing ROOT from RPMs:

```   
sudo yum install root.x86_64
sudo yum install root-gui-qt.x86_64
```

Prerequisites --> installing QT4 from sources, after untaring the archive (qt 4.8.7):

```
./configure -prefix <installation point> -qt-sql-oci -plugin-sql-oci -v -opensource -confirm-license -nomake examples -nomake tests -system-libjpeg -system-zlib -system-libpng -system-libtiff  -system-libmng -I/opt/xdaq/include/ -L/opt/xdaq/lib/ 	
gmake
gmake install
```

Download and compile tkCommissioner: make sure to properly edit the set_environment.sh to poin to the right QTDIR

```
git clone git@github.com:trackerpro/TkCommissioner.git -b newCommissioner_cc7_developments 
set_environment.sh
qmake
make		
```